#HAVE EMPTY dataset AND trainer FOLDERS BEFORE RUNNING facedataset.py, HAVE haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml IN SAME FOLDER AS PROGRAM#

1.Use facedataset.py to create a dataset of the face you want recognised and enter an id number 1 larger than the last(starting at 1)
2.Use facetraining.py to create a yml file from the data
3.in facerecognition.py add the name of the person in the names array in the order of ID number
4.Run facerecognition.py and the program will try to find the best match for the face it's presented and prints the name into user.txt
